  "body": "1. ~On Android, trying to update the status bar visiblity using `mergeOptions` causes the screen to flicker:~\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29354102/225046572-7b63afef-f800-4206-94d0-01d288d93ce6.mp4\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n2. ~Doing the same, with `translucent` and `drawBehind` set to `true` will cause the content to be pushed down:~\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29354102/225049358-fe7199fc-5974-40fd-8ab4-eaef4d9f7c89.mp4\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n3. On iOS, setting animate to `true` has no effect (both using mergeOptions, and when setting options when defining the screen). \r\n\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRelated issue: https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/15260",
